tus.src:
TachiyomiJ2K requires access to all files in Android 11 to download chapters, create automatic backups, and read local manga. 

On the next screen, enable "Allow access to manage all files."
tus.tgt:
在 Android 11 中，TachiyomiJ2K 需要访问所有文件才能下载章节、创建自动备份和阅读本地漫画。 
 
在下一个屏幕上，启用“允许访问管理所有文件”

This extension was signed with an untrusted certificate and wasn't activated.

A malicious extension could read any login credentials stored in Tachiyomi or execute arbitrary code.

By trusting this certificate you accept these risks.

信任这个证书，即代表你愿意承担上述风险。
